{
  "id": "69b0e0c9feb5b51b0e7b9853",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:AIスロップ",
  "created": 1773199596,
  "updated": 1773199641,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b0e0c9feb5b51b0e7b9853",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:AIスロップ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199596,
      "updated": 1773199596
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0eb00000000003dfa6a",
      "text": "[AIスロップ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199596,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa6c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa6d",
      "text": "やっほー！今日は「AIスロップ」ってテーマでだべろうぜ〜。最近タイムラインでもめっちゃ見るんだよね、このワード。なんか「AIが作ったビミョーなコンテンツ大量発生」みたいな意味らしいんだけど、ぶっちゃけみんなどう思う？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa6e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa6f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa70",
      "text": "そうねぇ……。最近、絵や文章を眺めておりますと、「あれ、これは人の手によるものかしら」と迷う瞬間が増えてまいりました。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa71",
      "text": "AIという新しい筆を人が手にした……そのようにも感じますけれど、一方で、あまりにも多くの作品が一度に生まれてしまうと、少しだけ、森の中で道を見失ったような気持ちにもなりますね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa73",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa74",
      "text": "「AIスロップ（AI slop）」は、生成AIによって低品質または大量生産されたコンテンツを指すネット用語。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa75",
      "text": "特に画像・記事・動画などで使われる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa76",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa77",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa78",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AI_slop",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa79",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa7a",
      "text": "要点を整理すると、問題は主に3つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa7b",
      "text": " 量が多すぎる（コンテンツ洪水）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa7c",
      "text": " 品質が低い場合がある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa7d",
      "text": " 人間の作品と区別が難しい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa7e",
      "text": "技術的には、生成AIのコストが急激に下がったことが原因。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa7f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa80",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa81",
      "text": "あーそれそれ！「コンテンツ洪水」ってやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa82",
      "text": "なんかさ、YouTubeとかでも「AI量産チャンネル」っぽいの増えてね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa83",
      "text": " ナレーションAI",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa84",
      "text": " 画像AI",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa85",
      "text": " 動画自動編集",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa86",
      "text": "みたいなやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa87",
      "text": "ぶっちゃけ「うお、量産型だ…」って感じのやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa89",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa8a",
      "text": "確かに……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa8b",
      "text": "本を読むときでも、心を込めて書かれた文章というのは、不思議と呼吸のようなものが感じられるものです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa8c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa8d",
      "text": "けれど、急いで作られた文章は、どこか風景のない道を歩くようで……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa8e",
      "text": "悪いというより、「少し寂しい」と感じる方もいらっしゃるのではないかしら。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa8f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa90",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa91",
      "text": "その感覚は理にかなっている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa92",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa93",
      "text": "AI生成文章は確率的に最もそれらしい文章を出す仕組み。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa94",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa95",
      "text": " 文法 → かなり正しい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa96",
      "text": " 情報 → それっぽい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa97",
      "text": " 体験 → 基本的に存在しない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa98",
      "text": "だから「魂がない」と言われることがある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa99",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa9a",
      "text": "ただし補足。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa9b",
      "text": "AI自体が問題というより運用の問題。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa9c",
      "text": "AI × 人間の編集",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa9d",
      "text": "なら品質はかなり上がる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa9e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfa9f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa0",
      "text": "あーなるほどね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa1",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa2",
      "text": " AIだけ → スロップになりがち",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa3",
      "text": " 人間チェック → ちゃんと作品",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa4",
      "text": "って感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa6",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa7",
      "text": "概ねその理解でいい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa8",
      "text": "実際、ソフトウェア開発でも同じ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaa9",
      "text": " AIコード生成 →",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaaa",
      "text": "  そのまま使うとバグ率が上がる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaab",
      "text": "でも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaac",
      "text": " AI + エンジニアレビュー →",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaad",
      "text": "  生産性は向上する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaae",
      "text": "GitHubの調査でも、AI補助で開発速度が上がるという報告がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaaf",
      "text": "https://github.blog/ai-and-ml/github-copilot/quantifying-github-copilots-impact-on-developer-productivity-and-happiness/",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab1",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab2",
      "text": "なるほど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab3",
      "text": "それは、まるで写本職人が新しい筆を手に入れたようなものかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab5",
      "text": "筆が便利になっても、美しい文章を書くには、やはり人の心が必要……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab6",
      "text": "そのように思います。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfab9",
      "text": "いい例えじゃんそれ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfabb",
      "text": "でもさ、もう一個気になるのがさ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfabc",
      "text": "「検索がAIスロップで汚染される」って話。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfabd",
      "text": "なんか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfabe",
      "text": "「調べてもAI記事ばっか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfabf",
      "text": "みたいなの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac1",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac2",
      "text": "それは実際に議論されている問題。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac4",
      "text": "理由は単純。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac5",
      "text": "AI記事は作るコストがほぼゼロ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac6",
      "text": "すると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac7",
      "text": "SEO目的サイト",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac8",
      "text": "↓",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfac9",
      "text": "AI記事を数万ページ生成",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaca",
      "text": "↓",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfacb",
      "text": "検索結果に大量出現",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfacc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfacd",
      "text": "という現象が起きる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dface",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfacf",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad0",
      "text": "https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/2/23707759/ai-generated-content-spam-google-search",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad3",
      "text": "うわぁ…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad4",
      "text": "まさにインターネットのスライム牧場じゃんｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad6",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad7",
      "text": "けれど、私は少しだけ希望も感じます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfad9",
      "text": "たとえば……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfada",
      "text": "人が丁寧に書いた文章、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfadb",
      "text": "時間をかけて描いた絵、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfadc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfadd",
      "text": "そうしたものは、不思議と見る人の心に残るものです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfade",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfadf",
      "text": "たとえ周りにたくさんの声があっても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae0",
      "text": "澄んだ鈴の音は、やはり耳に届くのではないでしょうか。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae3",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae5",
      "text": "歴史的に見ても",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae6",
      "text": " 写真の登場 → 絵画が終わると言われた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae7",
      "text": " 電子書籍 → 紙の本が終わると言われた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae8",
      "text": "しかし実際は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfae9",
      "text": "役割が変化しただけ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaea",
      "text": "AIも同じ可能性が高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaeb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaec",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaed",
      "text": "まとめるとこんな感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaef",
      "text": "📌今日のAIスロップまとめ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf0",
      "text": " AIでコンテンツ量が爆増",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf1",
      "text": " そのせいで低品質の量産も増える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf2",
      "text": " でもAI自体は悪じゃない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf3",
      "text": " 人間と組み合わせるとむしろ強い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf4",
      "text": "ってことだよね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf6",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf7",
      "text": "正確。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaf9",
      "text": "最後に補足。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfafa",
      "text": "今のネットは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfafb",
      "text": " 「AIで作る時代」から",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfafc",
      "text": " 「AIをどう使うかの時代」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfafd",
      "text": "に移行している。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfafe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfaff",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb00",
      "text": "なんだか、時代の川を眺めているようですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb01",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb02",
      "text": "水の流れはとても速いけれど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb03",
      "text": "その川辺で、ゆっくり本を読む人もきっといる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb04",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb05",
      "text": "そんな場所が、これからも残ってくれると嬉しいですね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb06",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb07",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb08",
      "text": "よし！今日はこのへんで！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb09",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb0a",
      "text": "みんなも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb0b",
      "text": "「AIスロップだらけじゃん！」って思ったら",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb0c",
      "text": " ちゃんと人が作ってそうな作品探す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb0d",
      "text": " お気に入りクリエイター応援",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb0e",
      "text": "とかするといいかもね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb0f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb10",
      "text": "インターネット、まだまだ遊び場だし！ 🎮",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb12",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb13",
      "text": "もしよかったら、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb14",
      "text": "この3人の鼎談シリーズで",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb15",
      "text": " 「AIとイラスト問題」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb16",
      "text": " 「AIはクリエイターの敵？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb17",
      "text": " 「AI時代の勉強法」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0ec00000000003dfb18",
      "text": "とかも作れるけど、やってみる？結構おもしろいテーマだよ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199597,
      "updated": 1773199597
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e10b00000000003dfb19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199627,
      "updated": 1773199627
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e10b00000000003dfb1a",
      "text": "#2026-03-11",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199628,
      "updated": 1773199641
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e10d00000000003dfb1b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199629,
      "updated": 1773199629
    }
  ]
}